{"tid":1523532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊罷搭狗鐵 拜託","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:12:02.000Z","uid":44655,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0efde371ea74c7c69f793a5a5f3914b56cee280a","tid":1523532,"uid":44655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zd3hxqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZd3hxqQ.jpg&h=7ca2673d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">831黑警</span>逐個站追擊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">市民</span><br />\n唔該全城罷搭狗鐵<br />\n無啦啦就可以放狗入黎拉你<br />\n你地真係想個個星期比狗打？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人反擊啦，一係跳閘一係罷搭，一齊試下用其他交通工具</span></span><br />\n<br />\n每個星期六日都有咁多手足被捕，我好撚心痛，拜託大家罷搭狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eaee5d79ec64240e1cd8ad9704cfbcff2d1746","tid":1523532,"uid":44655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:54:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f256f47d0db9184ae3f3452d9b11d3b742fc4f2","tid":1523532,"uid":44655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:54:48.000Z","msg":"香港人要加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d44abf55874287cd9365b37d1ed1e8f1d276519","tid":1523532,"uid":44655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"我仲想煲底下除口罩相見"},{"pid":"6cf467b35d31be5e29edc8d72fe7b007b708a8ee","tid":1523532,"uid":44655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1e2252ce142e75765e1e29c25d733c0c798705","tid":1523532,"uid":44655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721=831</span></span>"},{"pid":"cf8c